data.description: Back to Active - seller financing fell through.  You could acquire this home for a low interest rate of 2.75% for qualified buyers!!! Welcome home!!  This beautiful home was originally a 3-bedroom rancher .  A second floor addition was added making it a 6 bedroom 4 Full bathroom  home.   It offers a unique combination of space, privacy and convenience ,  with a finished basement that can be used as a completely separate living quarters .  This property has the potential to generate additional income or provide a comfortable space for extended families.  1st Floor consists of 3 bedrooms,  living room , kitchen and full bathroom with handicap accessibility.  2nd consists of 3 more bedrooms and 2 more bathrooms.  Finished basement has a full bar and another full bathroom .  Enjoy the backyard oasis that includes an above ground pool, all concrete patio (no need for mowing front nor back) and gorgeous flowerbeds.  A detached garage makes for great storage or for one car.   Tesla Solar panel keeps the cost of electricity down .  AprilAire filter in place - which captures airbourne viruses and allergens.  Hardwood floors under carpets in downstairs bedrooms.   What more can you ask for..oh  wait .. a  1 year home warranty AND a $3,000 seller assist!!!    Schedule your showing today!!
